
<p>Principal Service:<br/>  104:25-37 <i>or</i> 104:25-32 <i>or</i> 33:12-15,18-22; <a href="bible:Acts+2%3A1-11">Acts 2:1-11</a> <i>or</i><br/><a href="bible:Isaiah+44%3A1-8">Isaiah 44:1-8</a>; <a href="bible:1+Corinthians+12%3A4-13">1 Corinthians 12:4-13</a> <i>or</i> <a href="bible:Acts+2%3A1-11">Acts 2:1-11</a>; <a href="bible:John+20%3A19-23">John 20:19-23</a><br/><i>or</i> <a href="bible:John+14%3A8-17">John 14:8-17</a></p>
<p><i>On the weekdays which follow, the numbered Proper which corresponds<br/>most closely to the date of Pentecost in that year is used. See page<br/>158.</i></p>
<p>Trinity Sunday:<br/>  93 <i>or</i> Canticle 2 <i>or</i> 13; <a href="bible:Exodus+3%3A1-6">Exodus 3:1-6</a>; <a href="bible:Romans+8%3A12-17">Romans 8:12-17</a>; <a href="bible:John+3%3A1-16">John 3:1-16</a></p>
<p><i>On the weekdays which follow, the numbered Proper which corresponds<br/>most closely to the date of Trinity Sunday in that year is used.</i></p>
